data.description: Seller has an Assumable 2.75% interest rate mortgage!!! Price Improvement!! Back on the market through no fault of the seller.   You must see this immaculately maintained end unit in the highly sought-after White Oak Preserve community! This beautiful 3 bedroom/3.5 bath home w/ a fully finished basement will stun you and have you ready to move-in! This is a Smart Home, equipped with smart thermostats, smart smoke/carbon monoxide alarm, garage door openers, cameras, and locks. Washer & Dryer included! Seller will buy home owner's warrantee.    Excellent Location!! Enjoy a community where luxury meets convenience, just outside of Atlanta with easy access to I-285, Truist Park and The Battery, close proximity to Restaurants, Shopping, Hospitals, and the Interstate. Walk or bike the Silver Comet trail or enjoy sports or the playground at nearby Oakdale or Shoupade parks. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a highly rated school district, perfectly nestled in a quiet community with access to all of the conveniences of city living.
